Under both growth conditions, cell width was found to increase with cell length. However, for cells in the approximately 3–7 μm range, increase in cell width was found to be minimal (≤0.2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
